==Cyrillic alphabet==
===Letter===
'''Ь''', '''ь''' (''italics: '''Ь''', '''ь''''')

#The thirtieth letter of the Russian [[Cyrillic]] alphabet. It is named '''мягкий знак''' (mjákhkij znak, or "soft sign") and it has no sound of its own, but modifies that of the preceding consonant, causing it to be pronounced soft (i.e., [[palatal]]ized). It is preceded by [[Ы]] and followed by [[Э]].

